Class DefaultNodeSettingsClassToNodeSettings

java.lang.Object
org.knime.core.webui.node.dialog.defaultdialog.settingsconversion.DefaultNodeSettingsClassToNodeSettings
public final class DefaultNodeSettingsClassToNodeSettings extends Object
This class is used to construct new NodeSettings to initialize them. For this the constructor of the given DefaultNodeSettings classes is called with the given context.
